{"title_page": "Uzhhorod", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2019}}\n{{Infobox settlement <!--more fields are available for this Infobox--See Template:Infobox Settlement-->\n| official_name                   = Uzhhorod\n| native_name                     = {{lang|uk|\u0423\u0436\u0433\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0434}}\n| other_name                      = \n| settlement_type                 = [[City of regional significance (Ukraine)|City of regional significance]]\n| image_skyline                   = Panorama of Uzhhorod.jpg\n| imagesize                       = 250px\n| image_caption                   = A panoramic view of Uzhhorod and the [[Greek Catholic Cathedral, Uzhhorod|Greek Catholic Cathedral]] in the centre of the image\n| image_flag                      = Flag of Uzhgorod.png\n| image_seal                      = \n| seal_alt                        = \n| image_shield                    = Coat of arms of the city of Uzhhorod.svg\n| shield_alt                      = \n| nickname                        = \n| motto                           = \n| image_map                       = \n| mapsize                         = \n| map_caption                     = \n| pushpin_map                     = Ukraine Zakarpattia Oblast#Ukraine\n| pushpin_label_position          = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n| pushpin_map_caption             = Location of Uzhhorod\n| coordinates                     = {{coord|48|37|26|N|22|17|42|E|region:UA|display=inline,title}}\n| subdivision_type                = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n| subdivision_name                = {{UKR}}\n| subdivision_type1               = [[Oblasts of Ukraine|Oblast]]\n| subdivision_name1               = {{flag|Zakarpattia Oblast}}\n| subdivision_type2               = [[Raion]]\n| subdivision_name2               = Uzhhorod Municipality\n| established_title               = Founded\n| established_date                = 9th century\n| leader_title                